### Toast Notification (with Icon)
- Appears when attempting to navigate past the first or last slide.
- Disappears automatically after a few seconds.
- Includes an **alert icon** for better visual feedback.
- **All text elements should use the Pretendard font.**

```html
<div id="toast" class="hidden fixed bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bg-theme-alert text-theme-text px-4 py-2 rounded shadow-md flex items-center space-x-2 animate__animated animate__fadeIn font-pretendard">
    <i data-feather="alert-circle"></i>
    <span>You cannot move further in this direction.</span>
</div>
```

